{"name":"聖白蓮","nameCn":"圣白莲","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/cc/b9/10805_crt_p3aa4.jpg","info":"<li><span>简体中文名: </span>圣白莲</li><li><span>别名: </span>被封印的大魔法使</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>勇往直前的僧侣</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>妖怪寺中的魔住持</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>超越灵长类的阿闍黎</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>ひじり びゃくれん</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Hijiri Byakuren</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>莲妈</li><li><span>性别: </span>女</li><li><span>种族: </span>魔法师</li><li><span>能力: </span>使用魔法程度的能力</li>","detail":"大人气同人系列游戏《东方project》的主要角色。首次出现在《东方星莲船》。 白莲在命莲死后，对人生苦短感到恐惧，想要求得永生长存。可惜通过佛力无法达成，白莲转而学习魔法与妖术保持青春。在与妖怪的接触中，她意识到妖力不强大是无法生存的，并且视为至理，逐渐在这条道上越走越深。一方面，她接受退治妖怪，另一方面又帮助妖怪，这就是她所认为的平衡。最终她的作为无法被人类接受，被封印到了魔界——与星莲船同音的圣辇船航向的目的地。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/50501","name":"東方心綺楼　～ Hopeless Masquerade.","nameCn":"东方心绮楼","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/fe/d9/50501_PXrPr.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/124268","name":"東方深秘録 ～ Urban Legend in Limbo.","nameCn":"东方深秘录 ～ Urban Legend in Limbo.","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/c8/c5/124268_L54c7.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/185318","name":"永远消失的幻想乡","nameCn":"永远消失的幻想乡","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/2d/10/185318_YUcff.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/1395","name":"東方星蓮船 〜 Undefined Fantastic Object.","nameCn":"东方星莲船","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/14/d9/1395_5nNvK.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/101989","name":"东方年代记 双姬蓬莱物语","nameCn":"","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/72/55/101989_wOACc.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/28035","name":"東方求聞口授　～ Symposium of Post-mysticism","nameCn":"东方求闻口授","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/p